scripts.build-prod: rimraf bundled-dist && rustup target add wasm32-unknown-unknown && cargo install wasm-pack && wasm-pack build --release --target web --no-typescript --out-name js-framework-benchmark-yew --out-dir bundled-dist && cpr index.html bundled-dist/index.html && (cd bundled-dist && rimraf .gitignore README.md package.json)
